title: Rolling Stones 91-98
description:
Here is fourth album with Rolling Stones. 
Cover, lyrics etc. 

Here is my fourth CD with Stones 
You can burn it on a 80 min or 700 MB disc. 
Use e.g. Nero. Open folder CD_3 and add all folders and files.

And you can unsophisticated help to reseed the contents anytime. 

Pls help me share. 
My capacity isn't so high. 

Did these albums under my convalescence after the second traffic-accident 1998. 
Got a new (bright) view of life. Lives and have a lovely wife and two marvellous daughters. 

Smile
